Steps followed to generate the GradCam heatmap for the CIFAR10 images.

Step 1:
Generate the RESNET18 Model follow the link given below.
(https://keras.io/examples/cifar10_resnet/)
Follow the file Resent_CIFAR10.ipynb for generating the RESNET model.

step 2:
Download the CIFAR10 dataset, and unpickle the files.
Store the image into the google drive in 32x32 pixel format.
Follow the file Load_and_save_CIFAR10_dataset.ipynb

step 3:
Go through the GradCam sample in the 
http://www.hackevolve.com/where-cnn-is-looking-grad-cam/
Follow the file Visualize_CIFAR10_classification_using_GradCam.ipynb
